二、Word 模板写法（关键）
你的 Word 模板里放 变量占位符
例如：

Test Report

Test Name: {{test_name}}

Test Duration: {{duration}}

Result: {{result}}

Screenshot:

{{screenshot_tls}}
三、Python 自动替换模板
最常用库：

pip install docxtpl
pip install python-docx
示例代码：
Python
from docxtpl import DocxTemplate, InlineImage
from docx.shared import Cm

doc = DocxTemplate("template.docx")

context = {
    "test_name": "TLS connectivity test",
    "duration": "5 minutes",
    "result": "PASS",
    "screenshot_tls": InlineImage(doc, "tls.png", width=Cm(12))
}

doc.render(context)
doc.save("final_report.docx")
生成结果：
Word 自动变成：

Test Name: TLS connectivity test
Test Duration: 5 minutes
Result: PASS
[截图]
四、自动截图（非常重要）
如果你的 pipeline 有网页或 dashboard，可以自动截图。
常用方法：
方法1 selenium

pip install selenium
示例：
Python
from selenium import webdriver

driver = webdriver.Chrome()

driver.get("https://dashboard-url")

driver.save_screenshot("dashboard.png")

driver.quit()
方法2 playwright（更推荐）

pip install playwright
playwright install
示例：
Python
from playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright

with sync_playwright() as p:
    browser = p.chromium.launch()
    page = browser.new_page()

    page.goto("https://dashboard-url")

    page.screenshot(path="dashboard.png")

    browser.close()
