六、自动生成报告 Pipeline
GitLab pipeline：

run tests
     │
     ▼
collect results
     │
     ▼
python generate_report.py
     │
     ▼
upload artifact
.gitlab-ci.yml
YAML
generate_report:
  stage: report
  script:
    - pip install docxtpl playwright
    - python generate_report.py
  artifacts:
    paths:
      - report.docx
